<div class="bordered-box">
  <div class="bordered-box__inner">
    <h3 class="bordered-box__title">The Strategy across the UK</h3>
    <div class="bordered-box__content">
      <p>As well as the UK Strategy, there are strategies for Northern Ireland, Scotland and Wales.</p>
      <ul class="list list--countries">
        <li class="list--countries-item">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list--countries-icon svg-icon svg-icon--country" focusable="false">
            <use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#svg-icon--uk"></use>
          </svg>
          <%= link_to 'Strategy for United Kingdom', '/', class: 'list--countries-link' %>
        </li>
        <li class="list--countries-item">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list--countries-icon svg-icon svg-icon--country" focusable="false">
            <use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#svg-icon--northern-ireland"></use>
          </svg>
          <%= link_to 'Strategy for Northern Ireland', '/', class: 'list--countries-link' %>
        </li>
        <li class="list--countries-item">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list--countries-icon svg-icon svg-icon--country" focusable="false">
            <use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#svg-icon--scotland"></use>
          </svg>
          <%= link_to 'Strategy for Scotland', '/', class: 'list--countries-link' %>
        </li>
        <li class="list--countries-item">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list--countries-icon svg-icon svg-icon--country" focusable="false">
            <use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#svg-icon--wales"></use>
          </svg>
          <%= link_to 'Strategy for Wales', '/', class: 'list--countries-link' %>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
